fields.name: Timber Semi Trailer
fields.description: In the forestry sector, Robinson aims to provide a wide range of transport solutions, amongst which (self-steering) trailer combinations, especially designed for the daily challenges of the wood sector. Our semi-trailers offer a very flexible and economic use, and are load independent. A high resistance welded frame, fixed or extendable, for transport of timbers or short woods, with or without forestry crane, mounted at the front or in the middle, with or without hydraulic steering system – shortly, a trailer designed according to the customers’ expectations.

fields.name: Timber Centre Axle Drawbar Trailer
fields.description: Robinson produces a range of centre axle drawbar skeletal trailer designs for our customers, suited to their independent requirements, with a large range of options, carefully designed to ensure a long life, low maintenance costs, whilst at the same time being user friendly. We aim to deliver low maintenance design with a high residual value.

fields.name: Timber Turntable Trailer
fields.description: The growing popularity of turntable trailers throughout whole Europe, has motivated Robinson to develop a range of turntable trailers. Developed for the core demands in the world of timber, the Robinson turntable trailers fit easily into the transport requirements of our customer. Our trailers are extremely manoeuvrable, combined with strong following characteristics. Meeting the customers’ expectations and needs, the Robinson turntable trailers are suitable for the most varied application in timber transport The particularly torsion resistant frame design in steel profile ensure a low depreciation with maximum lifespan.

fields.name: Timber Semi Trailer with Crane
fields.description: Robinson cranes, which are designed for professional use, combine the latest advances in crane technology, components and manufacturing materials. Robinson cranes have been designed to deal with a demanding industry that requires durability. A Robinson crane is a multi-functional and cost effective piece of equipment that can be used across different sectors. Flexibility, innovation and customer responsiveness make it possible for Robinson to work directly with the industry to provide solutions for evolving and demanding needs. The Robinson crane range produces excellent performance to weight ratios which assist our customers to run cost effective activities. The design and manufacture of our cranes is geared towards quality, durability and a long operational life. This contributes to continuous service to its’ owners and a strong resale value. When purchasing a Robinson crane, customers are entering into a long term partnership that will stand the test of time.

fields.name: Platform Trailer
fields.description: Platform trailers are often considered trailers requiring little design input compared to other trailers. However, Robinson is dedicated to manufacturing a wide range of platform trailers, designed and engineered to our customers’ specific needs. By finding out what our customers’ needs are exactly, we can deliver platform trailers that combine a variety of operational, design and safety features.
